                                                    <p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
                                                    <a href="http://www.twitter.com/Tolerance_UK"><img
                                                            src="http://twitter-badges.s3.amazonaws.com/follow_me-a.png"
                                                            alt="Follow Tolerance_UK on Twitter"></a>

                                                    <div align="center">&nbsp;</div>
                                                    <div align="center"><a name="queen" title="queen"></a><strong><span
                                                                style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS','sans-serif'">A
                                                                GREEN PRESENT FROM HER MAJESTY THE QUEEN</span></strong>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div align="center">&nbsp;</div>
                                                    <div align="center">&nbsp;<p style="line-height: 150%"
                                                            class="MsoNormal"><span
                                                                style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;">The
                                                                <a href="http://ukinperu.fco.gov.uk/en"
                                                                    target="_blank">British Embassy in </a> </span><a
                                                                href="http://ukinperu.fco.gov.uk/en"
                                                                target="_blank"><span
                                                                    style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;">Peru</span></a>
                                                            <span
                                                                style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;">
                                                                goes green to celebrate Her Majesty the Queen's birthday
                                                                by joining </span><span
                                                                style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;">Tolerance</span><span
                                                                style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;">
                                                                International's Human and Habitat Campaign.</span></p>
                                                        <p style="line-height: 150%" class="MsoNormal"><span
                                                                style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;">The
                                                                invitation sent to all guests invited reads, “This year,
                                                                as part of our activities to challenge Climate Change,
                                                                the embassy will make the Queen's birthday celebrations
                                                                carbon neutral. </span><span
                                                                style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;">Tolerance</span><span
                                                                style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;">
                                                                International will be calculating the CO2 emissions
                                                                resulting from the event and these will be offset by
                                                                supporting the reforestation project of </span><span
                                                                style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;">Tolerance</span><span
                                                                style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;">
                                                                International in the Amazon.</span></p>
                                                        <p style="line-height: 150%" class="MsoNormal"><span
                                                                style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;">The
                                                                embassy appreciates the kindness of our guests who have
                                                                traditionally sent flowers for this occasion but would
